    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="引言"><a href="#引言" class="headerlink" title="引言"></a>引言</h1><p><strong>第九届艺术金融年会在山东工商学院举行</strong></p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="活动宣传海报"><a href="#活动宣传海报" class="headerlink" title="活动宣传海报"></a>活动宣传海报</h2><img src="https://ricxx-1257022957.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/web/images/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B9%9D%E5%B1%8A%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B9%B4%E4%BC%9A/%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%AE%E9%A2%84%E5%91%8A%E6%B5%B7%E6%8A%A5.webp" width=42% hight=42%><h1 id="活动内容"><a href="#活动内容" class="headerlink" title="活动内容"></a>活动内容</h1><p><strong>很荣幸能参加本次活动，以下是部分活动内容</strong></p><h2 id="学术进行时"><a href="#学术进行时" class="headerlink" title="学术进行时"></a>学术进行时</h2><p>演讲者们分别从不同角度，详细的解释了数字资产，数字艺术与资产的关系等。<br>内容丰富且详细，全面，值得研究.</p><h3 id="学术现场"><a href="#学术现场" class="headerlink" title="学术现场"></a>学术现场</h3><img src="https://ricxx-1257022957.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/web/images/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B9%9D%E5%B1%8A%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B9%B4%E4%BC%9A/IMG_20230923_131744.jpg" width=75% hight=75%><hr><img src="https://ricxx-1257022957.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/web/images/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B9%9D%E5%B1%8A%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B9%B4%E4%BC%9A/IMG_20230923_133317.jpg" width=75% hight=75%><img src="https://ricxx-1257022957.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/web/images/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B9%9D%E5%B1%8A%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B9%B4%E4%BC%9A/IMG_20230923_134923.jpg" width=75% hight=75%><hr><img src="https://ricxx-1257022957.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/web/images/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B9%9D%E5%B1%8A%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B9%B4%E4%BC%9A/IMG_20230923_140248.jpg" width=75% hight=75%><img src="https://ricxx-1257022957.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/web/images/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B9%9D%E5%B1%8A%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B9%B4%E4%BC%9A/IMG_20230923_141437.jpg" width=75% hight=75%><hr><img src="https://ricxx-1257022957.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/web/images/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B9%9D%E5%B1%8A%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B9%B4%E4%BC%9A/IMG_20230923_142608.jpg" width=75% hight=75%><img src="https://ricxx-1257022957.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/web/images/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B9%9D%E5%B1%8A%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B9%B4%E4%BC%9A/IMG_20230923_142713.jpg" width=75% hight=75%><hr><img src="https://ricxx-1257022957.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/web/images/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B9%9D%E5%B1%8A%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B9%B4%E4%BC%9A/IMG_20230923_144953.jpg" width=75% hight=75%><hr><img src="https://ricxx-1257022957.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/web/images/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B9%9D%E5%B1%8A%E8%89%BA%E6%9C%AF%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E5%B9%B4%E4%BC%9A/IMG_20230923_170918.jpg" width=75% hight=75%>]]></content>
    
    
