    <title>今天我们光荣退役！！！</title>
    <link href="/2023/09/22/%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E5%85%89%E8%8D%A3%E9%80%80%E5%BD%B9/"/>
    <url>/2023/09/22/%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E5%85%89%E8%8D%A3%E9%80%80%E5%BD%B9/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="写在开头"><a href="#写在开头" class="headerlink" title="写在开头"></a>写在开头</h1><pre><code class="hljs">我们的故事以军训开始......    19天的锤炼，造就新一代山商人不屈的品格......</code></pre><p>但是今天，我们光荣退役！！！</p><span id="more"></span><h1 id="今日"><a href="#今日" class="headerlink" title="今日"></a>今日</h1><h2 id="我们沐浴在山商的阳光下"><a href="#我们沐浴在山商的阳光下" class="headerlink" title="我们沐浴在山商的阳光下"></a>我们沐浴在山商的阳光下</h2><p>同学们激动地等待着汇演的开始！<br><img src="https://ricxx-1257022957.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/web/images/OVER/IMG_20230922_073246.jpg" alt="军训汇演">  </p><h2 id="汇演领导发言现场"><a href="#汇演领导发言现场" class="headerlink" title="汇演领导发言现场"></a>汇演领导发言现场</h2><p>此时一位小伙举起了镜头……<br><img src="https://ricxx-1257022957.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/web/images/OVER/IMG_20230922_085352.jpg" alt="发言现场"></p><h2 id="英姿飒爽的自训教官"><a href="#英姿飒爽的自训教官" class="headerlink" title="英姿飒爽的自训教官"></a>英姿飒爽的自训教官</h2><p><img src="https://ricxx-1257022957.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/web/images/OVER/weixin_20230922201110.jpg" alt="自训教官">  </p><h1 id="训练时光"><a href="#训练时光" class="headerlink" title="训练时光"></a>训练时光</h1><h2 id="第一方队方队长"><a href="#第一方队方队长" class="headerlink" title="第一方队方队长"></a>第一方队方队长</h2><p><img src="https://ricxx-1257022957.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/web/images/OVER/IMG_20230920_173012.jpg" alt="方队长">  </p><h2 id="训练结束的随拍"><a href="#训练结束的随拍" class="headerlink" title="训练结束的随拍"></a>训练结束的随拍</h2><p><img src="https://ricxx-1257022957.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/web/images/OVER/mmexport1694791197483.jpg" alt="随拍">  </p><h2 id="小夕阳"><a href="#小夕阳" class="headerlink" title="小夕阳"></a>小夕阳</h2><p><img src="https://ricxx-1257022957.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/web/images/OVER/IMG_20230915_171238.jpg" alt="小夕阳">  </p><h1 id="最后"><a href="#最后" class="headerlink" title="最后"></a>最后</h1><h3 id="结尾曲"><a href="#结尾曲" class="headerlink" title="结尾曲"></a>结尾曲</h3><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width=330 height=86 src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=2022116424&auto=1&height=66"></iframe>]]></content>
    
    
